snippet.title: NBA 2K18 - Shaq Legend Edition Announcement
snippet.description:
Who takes the mantle as the next NBA 2K Legend Edition cover athlete? None other than Shaquille O'Neal! Watch his speech here. 

Pre-order the NBA 2K18 Legend Edition or Legend Edition Gold today:  http://2kgam.es/PreorderNBA2K18
